"This returns a combination of both the alerts in the page and in the request"| alertSet |alertSet _ Set new."Add alerts found in page"((page settingsAt: 'alerts' ifAbsent: ['']) findTokens: String crlf, ' ;,') do: [:token |	alertSet add: token]."Add alerts found in request"((request fieldsKey: 'alerts') findTokens: String crlf, ' ;,') do: [:token |	alertSet add: token].String streamContents: [:stream |	"Put Addresses Back Together"	alertSet do: [:address | stream nextPutAll: (TextFormatter encodeToXmlCrlf: address)]		separatedBy: [stream nextPutAll: ' ']]